      <title>机器学习——k近邻(k-NN)算法</title>
      <link>https://eternityqjl.github.io/blog2_public/posts/%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0k%E8%BF%91%E9%82%BB-k-nn-%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95/</link>
